Package jadex.testcases.misc

This package contains miscellaneous testcases.

See:
          Description

Capabilities
ConfigElementRefWorker Check naming of referenced config elements Part of ConfigElementRef test.
DynamicModelCreation
EndStateWorker Check usage of end elements in capabilities Part of EndState test.
 

Agents

Arguments Agent for testing agent arguments.

Callback Agent for testing agent callbacks.

ConfigElementRefWorker Test referencing config elements by name.
DFMobile Test the mobile DF capability.
DFTest Test the DF capability.
DynamicModelCreation Test the creation of model elements at runtime.

EndStateDeregister Register in initial state and deregister in end state.

Leaker Test, if cleaning up works properly.
ParameterProtection Test the protection of parameter directions.
Repeatability Test the repeatability of agent execution.
Serialization An agent that tries to serialize itself.
WaitFor Agent for testing various waitFor methods.
